_:N3c83a88c697d46c69f3946050a997f89 <http://schema.org/name> "About us" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:N3c83a88c697d46c69f3946050a997f89 <http://schema.org/text> "HM Nautical Almanac Office is a small multi-disciplinary group of specialists whose purpose is to provide solutions to astronomical and celestial navigation problems." <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:N3c83a88c697d46c69f3946050a997f89 <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:N3c83a88c697d46c69f3946050a997f89 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<p>We produce astronomical data suitable for a wide range of users, including professional and amateur astronomers, mariners, aviators, surveyors, the armed forces, the police, lawyers, schools and the general public.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>Founded in 1831, HMNAO was formerly part of the Royal Greenwich Observatory (based in Herstmonceux and then Cambridge).</p>\n\n<p>The UKHO took over the responsibility for HMNAO from April 2006.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-responsibilities\">Our responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p>We produce and provide:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>almanacs for astronomers, mariners, land surveyors and aviators</li>\n  <li>sight reduction tables for navigation</li>\n  <li>celestial navigation software (NavPac)</li>\n  <li>expert witness testimony for the police and legal profession</li>\n  <li>web services</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Web services include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>rise/set times of the Sun, Moon and Planet positions and configurations</li>\n  <li>Islamic prayer times</li>\n  <li>moon phases</li>\n  <li>equinoxes and solstices</li>\n  <li>predictions of the first sighting of the new crescent moon</li>\n  <li>eclipses of the Sun and Moon</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>To access our products and services please contact <a href=\"mailto:CustomerServices@UKHO.gov.uk\">CustomerServices@UKHO.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
